name: Untitled Dino Game
description:
Untitled Dino Game is a game jam project (made in 3 days) in which you guide Chompy the dino to the end of the track using planks to bridge the gaps. The player goes through 3 types of biomes to get to the beach zone to win the game. 

Made by:

Programmers:

- Luka Verhelle

Artists:

- Jasper Mathy

- Maxime Wouters

- Jerke Volckaert

- Remko Lyckx

- Tamy Popelier
